        },
        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A bloatmage: his blood is his power. Each spell he casts above 5th rank deals him @Damage[1d6[bleed]] (already in his HP); when he bleeds, his next spell gains +1 to its DC. Bleed effects <em>against</em> him are dire: the DC to stanch his hemophiliac wounds is +5, and each new bleed drains the blood pool that fuels his free castings.</p>"
        },
